## TECH STACK — FINAL, TIDAK BOLEH DIUBAH TANPA PERSETUJUAN FOUNDER

| Komponen         | Teknologi                        |
|------------------|----------------------------------|
| Frontend         | Next.js 14+ (App Router)         |
| Language         | TypeScript — WAJIB, bukan JS     |
| Styling          | Tailwind CSS                     |
| Database & Auth  | Supabase                         |
| Orchestrator     | n8n (self-hosted)                |
| AI Vision        | Gemini Flash 2.0 (Agent 1)       |
| AI Text          | TBD — free tier (Agent 2 & 3)    |
| Image Generation | Wavespeed API — Nano Banana 2    |
| Payment          | Mayar.id                         |

Jangan pernah menyarankan stack alternatif kecuali diminta founder secara eksplisit.

