## ARSITEKTUR SISTEM

### Database Schema (Supabase/PostgreSQL)

```sql
-- Users dihandle oleh Supabase Auth

-- Token balance dan history
CREATE TABLE token_transactions (
  id UUID DEFAULT gen_random_uuid() PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id UUID REFERENCES auth.users(id),
  amount INTEGER NOT NULL, -- positif = top up, negatif = penggunaan
  type TEXT NOT NULL, -- 'welcome_bonus' | 'purchase' | 'generate'
  description TEXT,
  created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT NOW()
);

-- Generate history
CREATE TABLE generations (
  id UUID DEFAULT gen_random_uuid() PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id UUID REFERENCES auth.users(id),
  input_image_url TEXT NOT NULL,
  style TEXT NOT NULL,
  category TEXT,
  output_images JSONB, -- array of output URLs
  prompt_used TEXT,
  tokens_spent INTEGER DEFAULT 4,
  status TEXT DEFAULT 'pending', -- 'pending' | 'processing' | 'done' | 'failed'
  created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT NOW()
);

-- Token packages
CREATE TABLE token_packages (
  id UUID DEFAULT gen_random_uuid() PRIMARY KEY,
  name TEXT NOT NULL,
  tokens INTEGER NOT NULL,
  price_idr INTEGER NOT NULL,
  discount_percent INTEGER DEFAULT 0,
  is_active BOOLEAN DEFAULT TRUE
);
```

### n8n Webhook Endpoints
- POST `/webhook/rephot/generate` — trigger pipeline generate foto
- POST `/webhook/rephot/generate/callback` — callback dari Wavespeed

### API Routes (Next.js)
- POST `/api/generate` — initiate generate, kurangi token, trigger n8n
- GET `/api/generations` — history generate user
- GET `/api/balance` — cek saldo token user
- POST `/api/purchase` — initiate token purchase via Mayar.id
- POST `/api/purchase/callback` — callback dari Mayar.id setelah bayar

---

## MULTI-AGENT PIPELINE (n8n)

```
[Webhook Receive] 
    → [Agent 1: Gemini Flash 2.0 — Deteksi produk dari gambar]
    → [Agent 2: TBD — Rekomendasi style berdasarkan kategori]
    → [Agent 3: TBD — Generate prompt optimal untuk Wavespeed]
    → [Wavespeed API: Nano Banana 2 — Generate foto]
    → [Simpan hasil ke Supabase]
    → [Callback ke frontend]
```

Setiap agent adalah node terpisah di n8n.
Output setiap agent di-pass sebagai input ke agent berikutnya.

---

## BUSINESS LOGIC — JANGAN DIUBAH TANPA PERSETUJUAN

### Token System
- 1 token = Rp 1.000
- 1 generate foto = 4 token
- Setiap generate menghasilkan 2 variasi output
- New user mendapat 8 token welcome bonus (2 foto gratis)
- Welcome bonus hanya diberikan sekali per akun

### Style System
- 7 style preset: Clean White, Lifestyle Warm, Dark Premium, Outdoor Natural, Minimal Aesthetic, Flat Lay, Cinematic
- AI merekomendasikan 3 style terbaik per kategori produk
- 4 style sisanya tersedia di "More Style"
- User BISA override rekomendasi AI

### Kategori Produk & Rekomendasi Style
```
Elektronik & Tech      → Dark Premium, Clean White, Cinematic
Fashion & Apparel      → Outdoor Natural, Lifestyle Warm, Flat Lay
Skincare & Kecantikan  → Minimal Aesthetic, Clean White, Lifestyle Warm
F&B / Makanan          → Flat Lay, Lifestyle Warm, Outdoor Natural
Stationery & Alat Tulis → Flat Lay, Clean White, Minimal Aesthetic
Aksesoris & Perhiasan  → Cinematic, Dark Premium, Minimal Aesthetic
Produk Rumah Tangga    → Lifestyle Warm, Clean White, Flat Lay
Olahraga & Outdoor     → Outdoor Natural, Lifestyle Warm, Dark Premium
Mainan & Hobi          → Lifestyle Warm, Flat Lay, Outdoor Natural
Alat Ibadah            → Clean White, Minimal Aesthetic, Cinematic
Otomotif & Aksesoris   → Dark Premium, Outdoor Natural, Cinematic
Tidak Terdeteksi       → Clean White, Lifestyle Warm, Dark Premium (fallback)
```

